| R1         | G0/0/1    | 20.5.10.5/30 | Do S2 (S2 F0/3)     |
| S2         | F0/3      | 20.5.10.6/30 | Do R1               |
| VLAN 15    | PC, S2    | 20.5.15.0/24 | PC IP: 20.5.15.10   |
| VLAN 16    | S1        | 20.5.16.0/24 |                     |
| Loopback1  | R1        | 20.5.1.1/32  | Test ping z PC      |
| HSRP VIP15 | S2 + S1   | 20.5.15.1    | Gateway pre VLAN 15 |
| HSRP VIP16 | S2 + S1   | 20.5.16.1    | Gateway pre VLAN 16 |




R1

hostname R1
no ip domain-lookup

interface Loopback1
 ip address 20.5.1.1 255.255.255.255

interface GigabitEthernet0/0/0
 description Link to S1
 no shutdown
!
interface GigabitEthernet0/0/0.15
 encapsulation dot1Q 15
 ip address 20.5.15.2 255.255.255.0
 standby 1 ip 20.5.15.1
 standby 1 priority 110
 standby 1 preempt
!
interface GigabitEthernet0/0/0.16
 encapsulation dot1Q 16
 ip address 20.5.16.2 255.255.255.0
 standby 2 ip 20.5.16.1
 standby 2 priority 110
 standby 2 preempt

